Module 4: tools to mitigate risk
Log: record of events within org system can identify

SIEM tools: collects and alalyze log data for critical activities in real time
- Splunk: self hosted tool
- Google's chronicle: cloud native
> dashboard to identify potential incidence and tell a story
playbooks: manual on how to respond
- chain of custody & protecting and how to protect and preserve evidence
network protocl analyzer (packet sniffer): capture and analyze data
- TCPDump
- Wireshark
linux OS
- open source OS, relying on CLI
programming language (SQL, python)
- automate with python
- SQL to filter data

Web vulnerabilities mitigation
- Antivirus software
- Intrusion Detection System
- Encryption
- Pen testing


